    (2024, 'Z_585', 'Global Exchange and Investment Attraction Support Program Call for Applications: 2024 Inbound Program for International VCs and Startups', '기타', '기타', '2024-08-16', '2024-12-31', 'Busan', '부산광역시', 'Busan Techno Park is pleased to announce the recruitment of international venture capital firms and startups for our 2024 inbound program. This initiative aims to build a strong foundation for foreign companies to enter the Korean market, specifically in Busan. We invite interested parties to apply and participate in this exciting opportunity.
Objectives - To identify and support foreign startups seeking to enter the Busan market, fostering job creation and foreign investment. - To attract international venture capital firms to establish local offices, thereby boosting venture investment in the region. - To support startups with innovative ideas and less than 10 years of operation, helping them establish a presence in Korea and contribute to the globalization of the domestic startup ecosystem.
Key Details - (Eligibility) Foreign startups or investors interested in establishing a branch or relocating their headquarters to Busan. *Startups must have been established for less than 10 years. - (Scale of Recruitment) 2 companies will be recruited - (Support) - Up to 20 million KRW, including 10 million KRW per company, provided in the form of vouchers. - Customized support including office space, legal, accounting, and visa consulting and acquisition support; business support through networking opportunities with domestic institutions and companies; communication assistance
Submission Apply via the Busan Startup Portal ( busanstartup.kr ) (open recruitment)
